title: CONSIDER GENETIC SCREENING
description: For patients with autoimmune disorders, we recommend a genetic screen as part of a comprehensive wellness strategy.

title: ASK QUESTIONS
description: Part of a comprehensive wellness strategy is not being afraid to ask questions.

title: SCHEDULE REGULAR CHECKUPS
description: One of the greatest things you can do for overall wellness is to schedule regular exams with your doctor.

title: MONITOR MEDICATIONS
description: Make a list and keep track of when your medications are due for refill.  Be prapred to share this list with any specialists.

title: CONSULT YOUR DOCTOR
description: Your primary care physician can be consulted on any medical questions you may have, aside from emergencies.

title: NOTE ALL OF TREATMENTS
description: Throughout your treatment process, take notes that you can refer back to at a later date.
